high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the oven, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean tomato.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left before the fridge to face the counter.
Put the clean tomato on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right, move a few steps forward, turn right and go to the sink
Pick up the tomato from the left side of the sink
Move back a little from the sink
Put the tomato in the sink, run the water on it, and pick it up
Turn to your right and to your left to face the counter to the right of the sink
Place the tomato on the counter
anns.task_desc: Clean a tomato and place it on the counter

high_descs: pick up the tomato to the left of the sink
put the tomato in the sink
wash the tomato in the sink then remove it
re-approach the counter to the right
set the tomato on the counter
anns.task_desc: clean the tomato on the counter in the sink then put it on the counter to the right
